data.description: LOCATION!! Minutes from Shopping, restaurants, The Trash Pandas stadium and Redstone Arsenal-  but quiet neighborhood!!! This beautiful craftsman style home has an open concept which is perfect for entertaining! Tons of natural light, the master bedroom is downstairs, screened in back porch creates a perfect setting for a relaxing night in!  Kitchen has built in breakfast nook, upgraded pantry, Kitchen island and huge laundry room! Open loft with 2 bedrooms upstairs. Amazing neighborhood great for walking, clubhouse, tennis courts, pool and more~
